INSERT INTO `kos_content` VALUES (1,'Welcome to Connected Schools','welcome-to-connected-school','','<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<p>This website is designed to support education in Cambodia. You will be able to access training materials to support various needs:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Complete professional skills such as mechanics, sewing, electricity, computer basics…</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> Agriculture training to support community development.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Various software and utilities useful to play content and ease your learning.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>This website will be enriched with more content soon.</p>\r\n<p>Please contact us to provide your feedbacks and express your training needs.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The Connected Schools project team</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><br /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">{besps}home{/besps}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','',1,0,0,0,'2010-06-12 11:54:06',63,'','2012-12-12 04:42:39',63,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2010-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','asterisk.png|left|Joomla! Logo|1|Example Caption|bottom|center|120','','show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=',79,0,29,'','Welcome to Connected Schools. This website is designed to support education in Cambodia. You will be able to access training materials to support various needs...',0,11730,'robots=\nauthor=',0),(38,'Professional Trainings','professional-trainings','','<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=4&Itemid=129\"><img alt=\"motobike\" src=\"images/stories/professional_training/motorbike_repair/img/motobike2.jpg\" height=\"56\" width=\"70\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 5px;\"><strong><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=4&Itemid=129\">Motobike Repair</a></strong></div>\r\n<span class=\"style7\">Practice based knowledge to maintenance and repair motorbike. Motorbike repair training describes the usage of common tools, the different part of the engine and their function and the electrical system of the motorbike. </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"border: none;\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"70\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=25&Itemid=161\"><img alt=\"sewing\" src=\"images/stories/professional_training/sewing/img/img_4.jpg\" height=\"60\" width=\"70\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 5px;\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=25&Itemid=161\"><strong>Sewing</strong></a></div>\r\nProvide learner with the basic knowledge to use standard sewing tools, operate and maintain sewing machine, various tasks to sew any clothe and describe a few standard model for Cambodia marketplace.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"border: none;\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"70\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=28&Itemid=167\"><img style=\"float: left;\" alt=\"makeup4\" src=\"images/stories/professional_training/make_up/img/makeup4.jpg\" height=\"51\" width=\"70\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 5px;\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=28&Itemid=167\"><strong>Beauty Salon</strong></a></div>\r\nProvide the learner theory and practice of nail decoration, Beauty Salon. Hair dressing lessons present the common tools, the basic technics and a variety of haircut models including some fashion ones.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"border: none;\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=487\"><img alt=\"office-2010\" src=\"images/stories/professional_training/computer_basics/img/office-2010.png\" height=\"61\" width=\"70\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 5px;\"><strong><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=487\">Computer Basics<br /></a></strong></div>\r\nAbilities to master standard computer operation in the office. Computer basic training consist of the following lessons: understand parts of the computer, how to type in Khmer and in English, operate task in Windows system and master the main functions in Microsoft Word, Excel and Powerpoint software.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"border: none;\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=18&Itemid=154\"><img alt=\"inetmail\" src=\"images/stories/professional_training/internet_email/img/inetmail.png\" height=\"49\" width=\"70\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td sty