re and process their food and key other techniques.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"border: none;\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"70\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=27&Itemid=165\"><img style=\"float: left;\" alt=\"home06\" src=\"images/stories/professional_training/pig_raising/img/home06.jpg\" height=\"60\" width=\"70\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 5px;\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=27&Itemid=165\"><strong>Pig Raising</strong></a></div>\r\nProvide the learner with the skills for small scale family Pig Raising. This content addresses both the sow, the fattening and the boar.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"border: none;\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"box_professional\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"70\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=33&Itemid=170\"><img style=\"float: left;\" alt=\"home06\" src=\"images/stories/professional_training/financial/img/home.jpg\" height=\"60\" width=\"70\" /></a></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 10px;\"><br /></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding: 4px;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 5px;\"><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=section&id=33&Itemid=170\"><strong>Financial Education</strong></a></div>\r\nFinancial Education training videos addresses youth in vocational schools, in other schools/university or in rural areas and low income families.<br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>','',1,2,0,13,'2010-08-11 08:28:22',64,'','2013-09-17 04:13:55',67,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2010-08-11 08:28:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','','show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=0\nshow_print_icon=0\nshow_email_icon=0\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=',299,0,1,'','',0,7705,'robots=\nauthor=',0),(46,'English Learning Method','english-learning-method','','<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"26%\"><img src=\"images/stories/english_method/engmethod1.gif\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n<td width=\"74%\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Straightforward is an integrated skills series with a transparent structure, making it an easy-to-use course for students and teachers alike.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: justify;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n<p>This multimedia content covers 12 topics per level.<br />Each level includes interactive activities in 5 categories: grammar, vocabulary, functional language, reading and listening. Activity types include gap fills, multiple choice and games. Each level includes a language reference which contains grammar notes and a word list which shows word frequency.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> To run the English training, you will have to download your preferred level on your computer and then extract it with a zip utilities (such as WinZip or 7zip) and finally double click on the MacMillan file.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a rel=\"shadowbox\" href=\"images/stories/english_method/beginner/MENUP.htm\"><strong>Beginner level</strong></a><em><br /></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a rel=\"shadowbox\" href=\"images/stories/english_method/elementary/MENUP.htm\"><strong>Elementary level</strong></a><em><br /></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a rel=\"shadowbox\" href=\"images/stories/english_method/intermediate/MENUP.htm\"><strong>Intermediate Level</strong></a><em><br /></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a rel=\"shadowbox