mer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ឬជាកន្លែងមួយសម្រាប់ឲ្យលោកអ្នកស្វែងរកការងារ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ធ្វើដោយខ្លួនឯង</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ទៅតាមបណ្តាលក្រុមហ៊ុនផ្សេងៗ។</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"CA\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ម៉្យាងវិញទៀតលោកអ្នកក៏អាចជ្រើសរើស</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">បុគ្គលិក</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">និងអាចដាក់ពាក្យ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ជា</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\">CV &amp; Cover Letter </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">នៅលើគេហទំព័រនេះក៏បាន។</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"CA\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.nea.gov.kh/\">http://www.nea.gov.kh</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"CA\">NEA </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ជាគេហទំព័រមួយ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ដែលផ្តល់ជូនលោកអ្នកនូវសេវាកម្មការងារ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">និងព័ត៌មាន</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">មានទីផ្សារការងារ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ប្រកបដោយ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">គុណភាព</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">និងប្រសិទ្ធិភាពដល់អ្នកស្វែងរកការបណ្តុះបណ្តាលជំនាញ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ការអប់រំ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">និង</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ការអភិវឌ្ឍន</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ព្រមទាំង</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">សាធារណជនទូទៅ។</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"CA\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">គេហទំព័រនេះបានប្រមូលនូវអត្ថបទ</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">និងព័ត៌មាន</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Khmer OS&quot;;\" lang=\"KHM\">ស្តីពីការប្រលងអហារូបករណ៍</