tion','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Car Electrical training explains to the learner the process electricity system in car, its different parts and their functions to operation of the car engine. These video content include Safety Work, Volmeter, Horn Sytem, Ignition System, Washer and Wiper System, Battery Charger System and So on..</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for_ hours including the practice time by the students.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The duration of the recorded video for this training is: hh-mm&nbsp; (theory: _ minutes&nbsp; and Practice:__)</p>','a795e907f5d8984a15e393c0e8eb014c','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5771,3,13,'sections','title','Chicken Raising','ae29c487d042a528d2d16a2683b3ed56','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5772,3,13,'sections','alias','chickendraising','9746b8f499b9df282a4ea75feefb7041','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5773,3,13,'sections','description','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The chicken raising content provides the learner with the knowledge to build poultry, understand anf process the chicken food, take care and understand hygiene requirements for the chicken, vaccinate and protect them from diseases.</span></p>\r\n<p><span> </span></p>\r\n<p><span>The teacher who delivers this training at Kampot Institute of Polytechnic for 168 hours including the practice time by the students.<br /> The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 9 hours and 2 minutes (Theory: 2 hours and 12 minutes / Practice: 6 hours and 48 minutes) <br /></span></p>','0bf7c95a6572273d3367b875b1f3f993','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5774,3,6,'sections','title','Computer Basics','f8aeffe4b2d3f89a5eb26e9f9a8cc703','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5775,3,6,'sections','alias','computer-basics','2273e8b7d38643b5ab9d427c4a3b3936','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5776,3,6,'sections','description','<p>The Computer Basic training consists of the core knowledge to use a computer: understand parts of the computer, how to type in Khmer and in English, operate task in Windows system and master the main functions in Microsoft Work, Excel and Powerpoint software. This video content provides the learner with standard computer skills to use in the office.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 120 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 10 hours and 06 minutes (Theory: 3 hours and 27 minutes / Practice: 6 hours and 39 minutes).</p>','b4681d20accb67deed3d695802acb9f2','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5777,3,7,'sections','title','Computer Repair','ab519ea4176477d7c760582db6e899f4','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5778,3,7,'sections','alias','computer-repair','ce3c3f643a7c6835d3786756a5736fd6','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5779,3,7,'sections','description','<p>Computer repair content provides the learner a presentation of all hardware components in a computer and the way they are connected to each other, the installation process of Windows operating system and several application software (Microsoft Office, Photoshop, CorelDraw…). Then it describes some key configuration and troubleshooting steps of a computer (configure BIOS and boot of the system, install drivers, Khmer fonts and anti-virus software, use a network, share a printer…)</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 120 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 9 hours and 28 minutes (Theory: 1 hours and 21 minutes / Practice: 8 hours and 07 minutes)</p>','15e44de953cf129d69bb6547c485f4ad','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5780,3,11,'sections','title','Electrical Motor','b8c11d4afe1f8f2f5e6126b845bd4fbe','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5781,3,11,'sections','alias','electrical-motor','ab5f6f91a28477fb5b17eda154f13045','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5782,3,11,'sections','description','<p>Electrical motor training explains to the learner the motor process, its different parts and their functions to operation the motor rotation. These video content include principle of motor, split phase motor, capacitor motor, shaded pole motor...</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 59 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is:​​ 03 hour 40 minutes (theory: 36 minutes and Practice:  3 hours and 4 minutes)</p>','4052ff9ee70ec608a3c774b428606ce3','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5783,3,9,'sections','title','Electrical Welding','4d299d739d3b5589adab8a3a622d66d9','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5784,3,9,'sections','alias','electrical-welding','ce84f66c4eec5c3c2668aeaadc076140','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5785,3,9,'sections','description','<p>Electrical welding training introduces the safety principles when operating electrical welding, describes the electrical welding principle with a focus on electricity current’s control and the process to use welding equipment to realize electrical welding of high quality standard.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 26 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 02: 06 minutes (theory:  36 minutes / Practice: 1 hour 45 minutes)</p>','c593e31ec344ae7e4cef6264bd4b4dd9','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5786,3,5,'sections','title','Electricity House Wiring','8026760eca8ecfb77db408f2b1da0ef9','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5787,3,5,'sections','alias','electricity-house-wiring','b4f7fa472adde85d0455df1148bba625','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5788,3,5,'sections','description','<p>Electricity house wiring training provides to the learner all the core knowledge to build the electrical network of a house: an understanding of conductor, cable-joint, fuse, lamp and their role, the usage of key devices for electrical measurement, the process to install and connect an electricity system in a house.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 120 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 7 hours and 35 minutes (Theory: 50 minutes / Practice: 6 hours and 45 minutes).</p>','f5587f9775a1b66e7cf4ce9690d995b6','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5789,3,1,'sections','title','English Methods','3a7db4a5e177b343ec97b05f09bdd52b','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5790,3,1,'sections','alias','english-methods','0fdbca469828abcebdf05f55e3dfbc50','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5791,3,1,'sections','description','<p>Select a news topic from the list below, then select a news article to read.</p>','68237b5a54b23d18de0f609967aabd27','','2011-12-30 11:35:48',63,0),(5792,3,14,'sections','title','Fish Raising','d8a16f07b9d3d1a5010b38a98f24a392','','2011-12-30 11:35:49',63,0),(5793,3,14,'sections','alias','fishraising','39c37a7fdc64337050e36fbee834ac59','','2011-12-30 11:35:49',63,0),(5794,3,14,'sections','description','<p><span>This training provides the basic technique to successfully raise fish: carefuly select the pond location, define and dig the pond, understand how to feed fishes, take care of the fish, manage the pond and other various techniques.</span></p>\r\n<p><span> </span></p>\r\n<p><span>The teacher who delivers this training at community across Cambodia for 1 week including the practice time by the students. <br /> The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 2 hours and 04 minutes (Theory:&nbsp; 1hour and 58 minutes / Practice: 05 minutes)</span></p>','65102deec0cf01fcbcfddf4ede147a5e','','2011-12-30 11:35:49',63,0),(5795,3,8,'sections','title','Gas Welding','034fd0809cbb16c4853db80e4a3f3a68','','2011-12-30 11:35:49',63,0),(5796,3,8,'sections','alias','gas-welding','80f774c406cb8445c2ae36ce4097dc5b','','2011-12-30 11:35:49',63,0),(5797,3,8,'sections','description','<p>Gas 