urces is forbidden.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><br /> \r\n<table style=\"height: 114px; border-spacing: 60px 0;\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"5\" width=\"800\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"150\" align=\"right\"><b>OUR SPONSOR:</b></td>\r\n<td width=\"300\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"images/stories/partner/sofronie.gif\" height=\"65\" border=\"0\" width=\"227\" /></td>\r\n<td width=\"100\" align=\"left\" height=\"79\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"150\" align=\"right\"><b>OUR PARTNERS:</b></td>\r\n<td width=\"300\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"images/stories/partner/MLVT.jpg\" height=\"114\" border=\"0\" width=\"100\" /><br />Ministry of Labor and Vocational Training</td>\r\n<td width=\"200\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"images/stories/partner/Don Bosco.jpg\" height=\"79\" border=\"0\" width=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><marquee behavior=\"scroll\" direction=\"left\">Connected Schools is thankful to Sofronie, a UK Charity Sofronie funds initiatives that help disadvantaged children build a better future for themselves. Sofronie has steadily supported Connected Schools program since 2010</marquee></p>\r\n<p><strong>Partners:</strong> This project is running in partnership with the Ministry of Labor and Vocational Training and with the cooperation of key partners to deliver the best quality resources.</p>',2,'advert1',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'mod_custom',0,0,0,'moduleclass_sfx=\n\n',0,0,''),(88,'IE6 Warning','We have included a script that will display a message to IE6 users advising them to upgrade to a more secure browser version. This is not enabled by default, but can easily be turned on or off with a toggle in the template index.php. When enabled, users visiting your site with IE6 only, will be able to view the message.',1,'user7',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'mod_custom',0,0,1,'moduleclass_sfx=\ncache=0\nfirebots=1\nrssurl=\nrsstitle=1\nrssdesc=1\nrssimage=1\nrssitems=3\nrssitemdesc=1\nword_count=0\nrsscache=3600',0,0,''),(89,'No Menu?','With the theme, in addition to the standard menu options of RokMoomenu, Suckerfish, Splitmenu and module, you can select an entirely new and useful option: none. As the word suggests, the switch will turn off the integrated horizontal menu in its entirety.',2,'user9',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'mod_custom',0,0,1,'moduleclass_sfx=\n\n',0,0,''),(90,'Front Banner','',2,'top',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'mod_banners',0,0,0,'banner_cids=\nmoduleclass_sfx=',0,0,''),(92,'Menu Styles','<p>Choose the perfect menu design for your site with 4 built in menu styles offering a variety of unique and colorful looks to compliment your color style. You can also choose from 3 different menu modes, or disable the menu bar completely.  <a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=31&Itemid=68\" class=\"readon2\">Read More</a></p>',2,'user11',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'mod_custom',0,0,1,'moduleclass_sfx=\n\n',0,0,''),(93,'10 Module Hilites','Construct the perfect assortment of color and whitespace with 10 included module variations allowing you to mix and match colors and styles for each of your blocks of content for that perfect look.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=18&amp;Itemid=32\" class=\"readon2\">Read More</a>',3,'user11',0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'mod_custom',0,0,1,'moduleclass_sfx=\ncache=0\nfirebots=1\nrssurl=\nrsstitle=1\nrssdesc=1\nrssimage=1\nrssitems=3\nrssitemdesc=1\nword_count=0\nrsscache=3600',0,0,''),(94,'Multi-Position Tabbed Modules','<p>Versatility 4 features the flexible Rokslide tabbed modules system, allowing for a total of 10 module based tabs. Each tab can contain multiple modules published to that position. You can also change the location of the tabbed modules block, with 5 different locations to choose from for maximum flexibility.</p>\r\n<p><input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><input id=\"jsProxy\" on