INSERT INTO `kos_sections` VALUES (1,'English Methods','The News','english-methods','articles.jpg','content','right','<p>Select a news topic from the list below, then select a news article to read.</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,0,12,'SlightShow=test\n\n'),(2,'Professional Trainings','Newsflashes','professional-trainings','','content','left','<p>fsafsdaf safsadfsa fsdasfd asfads sadfsad fasdfasfadsfas asfasfas</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',2,0,3,''),(3,'Academic Subjects','Frequently Asked Questions','academic-subjects','pastarchives.jpg','content','left','',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',3,0,1,''),(4,'Motorbike Repair','','motobike-repair','','content','left','<p>Motorbike repair training provides the learner with the knowledge of repairing motorbike engine and elecrical system. Its content describes the common tools to use, the different parts of the engine (cylinder, semi-piston, and carburetor), their function and maintenance process ad the electrical parts of the motorbike, from starter to light.<br /><br />The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 190 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is around 19 hours 54 minitutes (Theory:&nbsp; 1 hours 58 minutes / Practice: 17 hours 56 minites)</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',5,0,63,'ListImage=0\nSlightShow=motobike_repair/motobike1.jpg;motobike_repair/motobike2.jpg;motobike_repair/motobike3.jpg;motobike_repair/motobike4.jpg\n\nactId=58\nTitleAct=Additional document Motobike Repair'),(5,'Electricity House Wiring','','electricity-house-wiring','','content','left','<p>Electricity house wiring training provides to the learner all the core knowledge to build the electrical network of a house: an understanding of conductor, cable-joint, fuse, lamp and their role, the usage of key devices for electrical measurement, the process to install and connect an electricity system in a house.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 120 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 6 hours and 55 minutes (Theory: 48 minutes / Practice: 6 hours and 7 minutes).</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',6,0,75,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=house_wiring/house_wiring1.jpg;house_wiring/house_wiring2.jpg;house_wiring/house_wiring3.jpg\n\nactId=59\nTitleAct=Additional document House Wiring'),(6,'Computer Basics','','computer-basics','','content','left','<p>The Computer Basic training consists of the core knowledge to use a computer: understand parts of the computer, how to type in Khmer and in English, operate task in Windows system and master the main functions in Microsoft Word, Excel and Powerpoint software. This video content provides the learner with standard computer skills to use in the office.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 120 hours including the practice time by the students.</p>\r\n<p>The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 10 hours and 06 minutes (Theory: 3 hours and 27 minutes / Practice: 6 hours and 39 minutes).</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',7,0,85,'ListImage=0\nSlightShow=computer_basics/office-2010.png;computer_basics/office-docx-logo.png;computer_basics/excel-2007.png;computer_basics/powerpoin.gif\n\nactId=60\nTitleAct=Additional document Computer Basics'),(7,'Computer Repair','','computer-repair','','content','left','<p>Computer repair content provides the learner a presentation of all hardware components in a computer and the way they are connected to each other, the installation process of Windows operating system and several application software (Microsoft Office, Photoshop, CorelDraw…). Then it describes some key configuration and troubleshooting steps of a computer (configure BIOS and boot of the system, install drivers, Khmer fonts and anti-virus software, use a network, share a printer…)</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 120 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 9 hours and 28 minutes (Theory: 1 hours and 21 minutes / Practice: 8 hours and 07 minutes)</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',11,0,95,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=computer_repair/cumputer_repair3.jpg;computer_repair/computer_repair1.jpg;computer_repair/computer_repair2.jpg\n\nactId=61\nTitleAct=Additional document Computer Repair'),(8,'Gas Welding','','gas-welding','','content','left','<p>Gas welding content introduces the safety principles when operating gas welding, describes the gas welding principle, with focus on process to start, stop and control fire during the work, the equipment required to operate gas welding with high quality standards and various welding options with or without adding copper.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 51 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 02:22 minutes (Theory: 46 minutes / Practice: 1 hours and 58 minutes).</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',12,0,84,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=gas_welding/gas1.jpg;gas_welding/gas2.jpg;gas_welding/gas3.jpg;gas_welding/gas4.jpg;gas_welding/gas5.jpg\n\nactId=62\nTitleAct=Additional document Gas Welding'),(9,'Electrical Welding','','electrical-welding','','content','left','<p>Electrical welding training introduces the safety principles when operating electrical welding, describes the electrical welding principle with a focus on electricity current’s control and the process to use welding equipment to realize electrical welding of high quality standard.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 26 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 02: 06 minutes (theory:  36 minutes / Practice: 1 hour 45 minutes)</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',13,0,43,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=electrical_welding/electrical3.jpg;electrical_welding/electrical1.jpg;electrical_welding/electrical2.jpg\n\nactId=63\nTitleAct=Additional document Electrical Welding'),(10,'Small Engine','','small-engine','','content','left','<p>Small engine training presents to the learner the common gasoline engines, the function and operating process of biele, piston, and carburetor parts and describes the small engine maintenance process.</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 62 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 6 hours and 51 minutes (Theory: 59 minutes / Practice: 5 hours and 52 minutes).</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',14,0,45,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=small_engine/small_engine1.jpg;small_engine/small_engine2.jpg;small_engine/small_engine3.jpg\n\nactId=64\nTitleAct=Additional document Small Engine'),(11,'Electrical Motor','','electrical-motor','','content','left','<p>Electrical motor training explains to the learner the motor process, its different parts and their functions to operation the motor rotation. These video content include principle of motor, split phase motor, capacitor motor, shaded pole motor...</p>\r\n<p>The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 59 hours including the practice time by the students.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is:​​ 03 hour 40 minutes (theory: 36 minutes and Practice:  3 hours and 4 minutes)</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',15,0,37,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=electrical_motor/motor1.jpg;electrical_motor/motor2.jpg;electrical_motor/motor3.jpg;electrical_motor/motor4.jpg;electrical_motor/motor5.jpg\n\nactId=65\nTitleAct=Additional document Electrical Motor'),(13,'Chicken Raising','','chicken-raising','','content','left','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>The chicken raising content provides the learner with the knowledge to build poultry, understand anf process the chicken food, take care and understand hygiene requirements for the chicken, vaccinate and protect them from diseases.</span></p>\r\n<p><span> </span></p>\r\n<p><span>The teacher who delivers this training at Kampot Institute of Polytechnic for 168 hours including the practice time by the students.</span></p>\r\n<p><span>The duration of the recorded video for this training is 9 hours and 2 minutes (Theory: 2 hours and 12 minutes / Practice: 6 hours and 48 minutes)</span></p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',17,0,15,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=chicken/ch_1.jpg;chicken/ch_2.jpg;chicken/ch_4.jpg;chicken/ch_6.jpg;\n\nactId=260\nTitleAct=Additional Document Chicken Raising'),(14,'Fish Raising','','fish-raising','','content','left','<p><span>This training provides the basic technique to successfully raise fish: carefuly select the pond location, define and dig the pond, understand how to feed fishes, take care of the fish, manage the pond and other various techniques.</span></p>\r\n<p><span> </span></p>\r\n<p><span>The teacher who delivers this training at community across Cambodia for 1 week including the practice time by the students. <br /> The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 3 hours and 36 minutes (Theory:&nbsp; 1hour and 53 minutes / Practice: 1 hours and 43 minutes)</span></p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',18,0,45,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=fish/img_10.jpg;fish/img_4.jpg;fish/img_5.jpg;fish/img_7.jpg;\\nfish/img_8.jpg;fish/img_6.jpg;\\n\n\nactId=261\nTitleAct=Additional document Fish Raising'),(17,'Air Conditioning','','air-conditioning','','content','left','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Air Conditioning introduces the safety principles when installing air conditioner. Describing the function of equipment in air conditioning system, explaining the process of air conditioning type such as Condenser, Evaporator, Welding, Vacuum and insert gas and circuit for air condition system. Moreover, Show the process of hang on air conditioning, and how to repair and maintenance with modern-technic.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 120 hours including the practice time by the students.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 8h 49mn&nbsp; (theory: 13 mn and Practice: 8h 36mn )<span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: DaunPenh;\" lang=\"KHM\"></span></p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',19,0,16,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=air_conditioning/image 1.jpg;air_conditioning/image 2.jpg;air_conditioning/image 3.jpg;air_conditioning/image 4.jpg;air_conditioning/image 5.jpg;\n\nactId=387\nTitleAct=Additional document air conditioning'),(18,'Internet and Email','','internet-and-email','','content','left','<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Internet and Email introduces the fundamental of internet and email, Describe on how to create personal email such as yahoo and Gmail. Explain more detail about how to search document online with popular search engine as well as downloading document. Moreover, Chatting programs also integrate in this training content as well.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The teacher who delivers this training at Battambang Provincial Training Center​ &nbsp;teaches for 15 hours including the practice time by the students.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 6 hours and 17 minutes&nbsp; (theory: 17 minutes and Practice: 6 hours )</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: DaunPenh; color: red;\" lang=\"KHM\">&nbsp;</span></p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',20,0,100,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=483\nTitleAct=Additional Document Internet and Email'),(20,'Car Electrical','','car-electrical','','content','left','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Car Electrical training explains to the learner the process electricity system in car, its different parts and their functions to operation of the car engine. These video content include Safety Work, Volmeter, Horn Sytem, Ignition System, Washer and Wiper System, Battery Charger System and So on..</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The teacher who delivers this training at Don Bosco teaches for 190 hours including the practice time by the students.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 8 hours and 53 minutes (Theory: 1 hour and 52 minutes / Practice: 7 hours and 1 minute )</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',21,0,36,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=470\nTitleAct=Additional document Car Electrical'),(22,'Excel 2010','','excel-2010','','content','left','<p>The duration of the video is 10 hours and 41 minutes ( Theory: 1 hour and 16 minutes / Practice: 9 hours and 25 minutes)</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',9,0,16,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=557\nTitleAct=Additional document excel 2010'),(23,'Powerpoint 2010','','powerpoint-2010','','content','left','<p>The duration of the video is 6 hours and 37 minutes ( Theory: 0 hour and 22 minutes / Practice: 6 hours and 15 minutes)</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',10,0,12,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=558\nTitleAct=Additional document powerpoint 2010'),(24,'Word 2010','','word-2010','','content','left','<p>The duration of the video is 9 hours and 18 minutes ( Theory: 0 hour and 58 minutes / Practice: 8 hours and 20 minutes)</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',8,0,23,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=556\nTitleAct=Additional document word 2010'),(25,'Sewing','Sewing New','sewing','','content','left','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Basic Sewing training provides the learner with the core knowledge to operate sewing tools, maintenance sewing machine. Then it explains how to make a hole button,&nbsp; measure shirt, trouser and skirt, draw using patron and sew some standard cloth models for Cambodian marketplace.</span></p>\r\n<p><span> </span></p>\r\n<p><span>The teacher who delivers this training at Kampot Institute of Polytechnic teaches during 560 hours including the practice time by the students.<br /> The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 37 hours and 04 minutes (Theory: 7 hours and 14 minutes / Practice: 29 hours and 50 minutes)</span></p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',16,0,13,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=259\nTitleAct=Additional Document Sewing'),(27,'Pig Raising','','pig-raising','','content','left','The Pig Raising training addresses both sow, fattening and boar. It is providing you with the most important knowledge in pig raising: pig selection and breeding, how to build a pig sty,&nbsp; how to provide enough food and water, how to take care, vaccinate and prevent diseases. It includes real videos of practice which show you how to take care of piglets during and after the delivery. The training also includes best practice sharing from a successful farmer.<br /><br />The Pig raising content was recorded with Mr. Hin La, pig raising teacher from Polytechnic Institute of Battambang and experienced farmers. The teacher delivering this training teaches for xx hours.<br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is around 5 hours 20 minitutes (Theory: 3 hours 45 minutes / Practice: 1 hours 35 minites)<br /><br />',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',22,0,7,'ListImage=0\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=642\nTitleAct=Additional Document Pig Raising'),(28,'Beauty Salon','','make-up-and-hairdressing','','content','left','Beauty Salon training addresses nail decoration, make up and hairdressing. This content helps you to learn the tools and skills for nail decoration. You will also learn the basics of make up including tools, natural make up and sexy make up which is popular for ceremonies. Hairdressing lessons demonstrate tools, basic technics such as how to do simple hair cut and how to clean hair, but also how to make hair straight, curvy and some fashion hairstyles.<br />This content has been recorded in cooperation with Pour un Souvire d\'Enfant (PSE), Sihanoukville Provincial Training Center and Cambodia Thai Skill Development Center. <br />The duration of the recorded video for this training is: 18 hours and 23 minutes (Theory: 3 hour and 06 minutes / Practice: 15 hours and 17 minutes)<br /><br />',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',23,0,38,'ListImage=0\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=643\nTitleAct=Additional Document Make up and Hairdressing'),(30,'How to use CS System','','how-to-use-cs-system','','content','left','Hello world!',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',24,0,0,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=742\nTitleAct=How to use CS System'),(33,'Financial Education','','financial-management','','content','left','<p>The first part of the content (from video 1 to 6) will help you to better manage your income and expenses so as to improve your live. Each video is a skit between two or three people: one of them tells about a financial issue and the other explains ways to better manage money.  The second part (from video 7 to 10) will help you to start a small business to get ready for it and increase your success likelihood. These four videos go step by step on how to start a business, each one focusing on a specific point. They have to be seen in the right sequence (7 to 10). This content has been recorded in partnership with A + B = 3, social enterprise created in 2005.   The duration of the recorded videos for this training is: 1 hours and 32 minutes.</p>',1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00',25,0,53,'ListImage=1\nSlightShow=\n\nactId=813\nTitleAct=Additional document Financial Education');
